Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.40,0:00:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.06,0:00:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to bother you so early\Nin the morning. We're the state police.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.90,0:00:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.78,0:00:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.82,0:00:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry but have you been\Nhome all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.99,0:00:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I went out for drinks\Nuntil early morning. What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.29,0:00:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about Director Heinemann,\NDr. Oppenheim and Dr. Boyer
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.25,0:00:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,from Eisler Memorial Hospital…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.42,0:00:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They died last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.34,0:00:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.27,0:02:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The crime scene has to be sealed off\Nfor the police investigation!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.31,0:02:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be difficult\Nfor the hospital's operation!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.52,0:02:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,-Don't let the press enter the hospital!\N-Please do not disturb the patients!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.53,0:02:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this an accident or a murder case?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.78,0:02:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,All three of them died at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.95,0:02:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be a murder case!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.87,0:02:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you with the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.58,0:02:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know anything related to the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.16,0:02:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.71,0:02:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not cross the police line!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.38,0:02:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I work here. I'm Kenzo Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.46,0:02:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.84,0:02:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't push!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.92,0:02:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see anyone suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.67,0:02:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, this is not the time--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.51,0:02:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.22,0:02:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma! They all…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.18,0:02:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.22,0:03:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone calm down.\NHow is the emergency care?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.18,0:03:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, we have patients\None after another in this busy time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.31,0:03:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Two patients are waiting for surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.19,0:03:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll join the surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.69,0:03:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take the patient\Nwith the head injury.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.19,0:03:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll check out the X-rays first.\NWhat's the other one?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.78,0:03:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a patient with a stroke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.53,0:03:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Doctor. Can you help\Nwith the investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.25,0:03:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.54,0:03:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand,\Nbut the initial inquiries are important.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.00,0:03:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know of anyone who has\Na grudge against the doctors?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.34,0:03:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A grudge?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.55,0:03:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The path you had planned as a doctor
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.72,0:03:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,is no longer possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.80,0:03:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.81,0:03:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.06,0:03:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.52,0:03:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's awful! Those kids…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.77,0:03:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The twins…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.44,0:03:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't find them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.12,0:04:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The sister's bed is empty, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.04,0:04:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We looked everywhere,\Nbut we can't find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.46,0:04:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What's…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.63,0:04:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.01,0:04:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He saved numerous people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.14,0:04:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We will remember him\Nfor his achievements forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.15,0:04:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Dr. Heinemann.\NMay you rest in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.11,0:04:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.15,0:04:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.74,0:04:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,-Eva…\N-Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.66,0:04:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's tough but hang in there--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.50,0:04:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.92,0:04:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring my father back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.64,0:05:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Breaks your heart, huh? Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.72,0:05:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.64,0:05:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been living her comfortable life\Nas the Director's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.56,0:05:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Suddenly, she's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.65,0:05:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The shock must be significant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.53,0:05:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you talking about this now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.40,0:05:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.15,0:05:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.03,0:05:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm from the state police\Nof North Rhine-Westphalia,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.66,0:05:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,police inspector Weißbach.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.83,0:05:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an unfortunate case.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.75,0:05:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, let me make an introduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.38,0:05:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,POLICE INSPECTOR LUNGE\NFEDERAL CRIMINAL POLICE OFFICE (BKA)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.71,0:05:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Officer Lunge from the BKA.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.46,0:05:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Your reputation as a genius doctor\Nis well-known.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.88,0:05:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No, your praise is too much.\NI'm still just a young doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.89,0:05:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you found out where the children are?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.31,0:05:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s more important is we found out\Nthe cause of death for the doctors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.90,0:06:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Their bodies tested positive\Nfor nitric acid poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.15,0:06:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Nitric acid…\NDo you mean muscle relaxant?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.03,0:06:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, you would know as a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.70,0:06:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But how did it happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.96,0:06:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,-From candies.\N-Candies?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.67,0:06:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We found the same candy wrappers
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.71,0:06:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,next to all of their bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.75,0:06:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We also found the same thing\Nin their stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.88,0:06:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We are wondering how three of them\Ngot the same candies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.31,0:06:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.72,0:06:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How would I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.77,0:06:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind that. What about the twins?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.60,0:06:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The investigation has been taken over\Nby the BKA from the state police.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.23,0:06:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-You can rest assured.\N-Wha…?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.74,0:06:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If we trace back,\Nthere might be a connection
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.03,0:06:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,between this case\Nand their parents' murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.41,0:06:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help but think\Nof the possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.95,0:06:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Their parents were killed after coming\Nfrom East Germany for asylum,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.16,0:06:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and the doctors from the hospital\Ncaring for the twins were killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.58,0:06:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This might be related\Nto political terrorism.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.59,0:07:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The children might hold the key\Nto solving the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.59,0:07:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you can find them\Nas soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.84,0:07:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We will do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.06,0:07:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.85,0:07:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He was kicked off the position\Nof Head of Neurosurgery before the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.27,0:07:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And his engagement\Nwith the Director's daughter was broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.61,0:07:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,However, he was drinking during that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.37,0:07:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He has an alibi…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.83,0:07:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you one thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.70,0:07:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing with your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.58,0:07:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this? I'm typing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.42,0:07:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.96,0:07:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm entering all the information\Ninto the disk in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.17,0:07:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If I press the key to find\Nthe information here,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.93,0:07:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,"Your praise is too much.\NI'm still just a young doctor."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.31,0:07:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,When I called Dr. Tenma a genius doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.39,0:07:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,he looked embarrassed and awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.31,0:08:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The police? Are they suspecting you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.32,0:08:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,There are reasons that I could\Nbe suspected.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.03,0:08:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't blame them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.82,0:08:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.\NThey hounded me with questions too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.08,0:08:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.33,0:08:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,When the heat is off for this case,\NI'm thinking of going back to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.17,0:08:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.63,0:08:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to Germany to study.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.84,0:08:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,After all these things,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.68,0:08:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized that a doctor's duty\Nis to save people's lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.39,0:08:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.68,0:08:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tired from all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.85,0:08:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Just so tired…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.90,0:08:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Buchner,\Neverything looks good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.07,0:08:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.57,0:08:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I go back to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.91,0:08:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.33,0:08:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The place will fall apart\Nif I don't get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.58,0:09:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,However, don't overwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.21,0:09:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're out, I will go for drinks
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.34,0:09:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and check to see if you're pushing\Nyourself too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.13,0:09:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.34,0:09:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.34,0:09:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true?\NAre you really leaving the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.27,0:09:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.56,0:09:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,A good doctor like you is rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.40,0:09:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't say you'll leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.15,0:09:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.36,0:09:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Buchner…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.83,0:09:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma. The Chairman wants to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.21,0:09:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,They are deciding on the successors\Nof the doctors who passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.92,0:09:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The important posts have been filled\Nwith the Director's people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.67,0:09:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like they're going\Nto overhaul everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.09,0:09:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that Dr. Eckener
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.26,0:09:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,will be sent to a small hospital\Nin Bavaria.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.85,0:09:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,-I see.\N-Dr. Tenma…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.10,0:10:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what the Chairman says,\Nplease hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.14,0:10:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We are all behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.65,0:10:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't leave the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.86,0:10:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.11,0:10:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Once again, I told you that\NI only care about competence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.95,0:10:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma, we are naming you\Nas the Chief of Surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.01,0:10:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,My life is crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.59,0:10:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I refused the Director's order and got\Nkicked off as Head of Neurosurgery,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.56,0:10:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and my engagement with Eva was broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.06,0:10:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It happened when I decided
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.52,0:10:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,to live my life without any hope\Nof promotion or advancement.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.07,0:10:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,My… My life is crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.21,0:11:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for meeting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.59,0:11:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear you were appointed\Nas Chief of Surgery. Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.39,0:11:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.85,0:11:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenzo, at my father's funeral,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.85,0:11:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,you wanted to comfort me, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.35,0:11:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, well…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.31,0:11:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.86,0:11:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I know a lot happened,\Nbut I want to be with you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.33,0:11:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.00,0:11:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.71,0:11:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.17,0:11:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be with you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenzo…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.51,0:11:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.43,0:12:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,NINE YEARS LATER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.52,0:12:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an update\Non the spinal tumor patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.56,0:12:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The paralysis seems\Nto have progressed rapidly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.02,0:12:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it. I'll do the surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.82,0:12:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.24,0:12:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare for the surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.20,0:12:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.08,0:12:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.58,0:12:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,When will this flood be over?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.83,0:12:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,1995, COLOGNE (GERMANY)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.04,0:12:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The Berlin Wall fell six years ago,\Nand I thought this world would change.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.25,0:12:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing good came out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.21,0:12:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,With European integration,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.30,0:12:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot of bad things came in from all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.09,0:12:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We have more crimes without reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.18,0:12:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.43,0:12:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector, we have arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.10,0:12:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The two bodies had their necks\Nslashed with a knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.48,0:12:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Their identities?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.69,0:12:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. and Mrs. Reichman,\Nwho live in Stech Lane.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.44,0:12:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They were found killed in their home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.57,0:13:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Their bodies were hidden in the closet,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.37,0:13:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and their bodies got\Nflushed out by this flood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.16,0:13:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Another murder of middle-aged couples.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.29,0:13:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We've had four in two years\Nin the whole country.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.87,0:13:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They were all killed in the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.84,0:13:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They are just robberies targeting\Nrich middle-aged couples.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.80,0:13:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's too early to assume\Nthey are just robberies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.30,0:13:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,From the data, I can't help but notice
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.39,0:13:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,that all the victims did not\Nhave children.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.68,0:13:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.\NThis couple didn't have children, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.68,0:13:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's just a series of robberies,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.94,0:13:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't this common point intriguing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.44,0:13:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,However, all the victims\Nhad items stolen from their homes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.94,0:13:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,There was limited damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.82,0:13:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If it were someone working alone,\Nthat might make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.16,0:13:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And if they weren't working alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.08,0:13:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Two of the houses had highly secured locks\Nand alarm systems.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.12,0:13:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the suspect easily\Ndisabled them and entered.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.92,0:14:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no evidence that the victims\Nresisted before being killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.17,0:14:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,None of the neighbors heard\Nany ruckus during the killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.18,0:14:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that too efficient\Nfor someone working alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.68,0:14:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.39,0:14:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know this man?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.02,0:14:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.15,0:14:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Adolf Junkers, age 32.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.77,0:14:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He had two prior arrests for robberies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.69,0:14:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a locksmith, and his job was\Nopening the lock for the robbery.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.78,0:14:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,In the past middle-aged couple murders,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.95,0:14:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,he was spotted near three\Nof the crime scenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.04,0:14:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So, is he the suspect?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.46,0:14:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.29,0:14:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case,\Nthis is it for you state police.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.80,0:14:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The BKA will take over from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.80,0:14:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.64,0:14:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I still can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.56,0:14:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never flown a kite.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.19,0:14:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You almost did it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.65,0:14:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,How was she last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.65,0:15:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a nice girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.19,0:15:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's the daughter\Nof a board member!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.90,0:15:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me you didn't just have dinner\Nwith her and say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.16,0:15:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,During dinner, I got called in\Nfor an urgent patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.49,0:15:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I came back to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.95,0:15:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.00,0:15:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop with the work comes first policy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.63,0:15:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll regret missing out\Non this good chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.84,0:15:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you listening? Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.92,0:15:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a kite?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.01,0:15:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.93,0:15:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Karl, is this yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.93,0:15:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,My grandpa gave it to me,\Nbut it doesn't seem to go up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.18,0:15:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe the center is off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.69,0:15:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, can you fly a kite?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.40,0:15:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to do it in my childhood in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.94,0:15:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it up high, Karl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.82,0:15:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.78,0:15:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.28,0:15:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see if this works!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.63,0:16:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.01,0:16:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.60,0:16:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well. If I were him,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.35,0:16:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll probably have five lovers already.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.15,0:16:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so good at it, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.15,0:16:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Get well soon, then next time\Nyou can do it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.24,0:16:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.66,0:16:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Today we're doing\Na parasellar meningioma extirpation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.13,0:16:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be using the right\Npterional approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.21,0:16:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.63,0:16:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.55,0:16:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The Chief Dr. Tenma\Nis personally operating.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.63,0:16:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This surgery is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.93,0:16:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He barely retracted the brain tissue.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.51,0:16:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a genius neurosurgeon indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.02,0:16:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You residents should remember\Nto be careful
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.64,0:17:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,when you operate on the patient's brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.43,0:17:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my god!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.77,0:17:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Call an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.19,0:17:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not me! It wasn't my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.69,0:17:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He ran in front of my car out of nowhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.16,0:17:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the patient?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.37,0:17:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.41,0:17:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.62,0:18:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There's little we can do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.62,0:18:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He is a person of interest in a case.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.79,0:18:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,From this man's testimony,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.54,0:18:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,we might just solve a series of murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.09,0:18:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let him die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.51,0:18:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But this patient's condition is dire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.76,0:18:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,In our hospital, there's nothing…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.39,0:18:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There is an excellent neurosurgeon\Nin Eisler Memorial Hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.77,0:18:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If he can come, he might survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.94,0:18:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,A neurosurgeon?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.40,0:18:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you mean Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.11,0:18:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.99,0:18:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How is the patient?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.95,0:18:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He is unconscious\Nand one of his pupils is dilated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.83,0:18:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Long time no see, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.13,0:18:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.09,0:18:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The last time I met you was\Nat the Director's funeral nine years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.09,0:18:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're from the BKA.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.30,0:18:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Police Inspector Lunge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.26,0:19:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you can help us at the BKA
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.56,0:19:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,by performing this surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.06,0:19:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.06,0:19:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This patient has to survive
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.27,0:19:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,for us to solve a case.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.48,0:19:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not doing surgery for the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.36,0:19:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing it for the patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.95,0:19:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.03,0:19:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to get to the surgery now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.04,0:19:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that you are now\Nthe Chief of Surgery, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.42,0:19:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite a promotion for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.25,0:19:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.55,0:19:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impressive when you're\Nstill so young.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.30,0:19:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be the next Director soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.05,0:19:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I still have a long way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.80,0:19:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There is still very little evidence
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.18,0:19:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,in the Eisler Memorial Hospital case.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.39,0:19:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The investigation has hit a dead end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.90,0:19:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The only clue we had, the poisoned candy,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.82,0:19:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,can tell us that it's\Nan intellectual crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.57,0:19:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's an intellectual crime,\Nthat means there's a personal interest
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.32,0:19:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,between the victim and the perpetrator.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.03,0:20:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.04,0:20:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.08,0:20:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just an occupational hazard that\Nall I think about is work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.00,0:20:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Please rest assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.21,0:20:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There is not a single case I took on\Nthat I haven't solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.05,0:20:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.89,0:20:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Best of luck to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.15,0:20:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll perform a craniotomy\Nto remove the hematoma.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.61,0:20:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to hurry, or there will\Nbe the risk of cerebral hernia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.99,0:20:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,After the Eisler Memorial Hospital\Nmurder case,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.99,0:20:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,one person profited immensely from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.04,0:20:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And that person…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.42,0:20:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,is you, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.51,0:21:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming all this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.14,0:21:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How is the patient after the surgery?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.72,0:21:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He is conscious now,\Nbut his right pupil is still dilated.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.94,0:21:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He is still paralyzed on one side.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.73,0:21:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He has already started\Nphysical therapy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.11,0:21:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he will get better. It looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.32,0:21:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The police might want to talk to him soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.36,0:21:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's not the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.78,0:21:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But that Officer Lunge is so persistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.83,0:21:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The patient's recovery\Nshould be the priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.30,0:21:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you feeling, Mr. Junkers?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.05,0:21:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Junkers, do you know who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.89,0:21:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you see my finger?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.31,0:21:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you answer me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.90,0:21:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.95,0:22:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Mr. Junkers?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.53,0:22:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,…coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.33,0:22:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming? What is coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.83,0:22:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mon… coming…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.46,0:22:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The monster… is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.22,0:22:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Monster?
